<h2>Pokémon Emerald: RNG Manipulation for 100% Completion</h2>

<div>
How to obtain the recommended Pokémon to complete 100% Emerald:
<ul>
  <li>Latios (for Battle Frontier)</li>
  <li>Metagross (for Battle Frontier)</li>
  <li>Swampert (for Battle Frontier)</li>
  <li>Kecleon (for Liechi Berry in Mirage Island)</li>
</ul>
</div>
<br>

<h4>Emerald RNG Mechanisms</h4>
<p>All recommended Pokémon for completing 100% Emerald are stationnary Pokémon.</p>
<p>The IV, ability, nature, and PID of stationnary Pokémon only depend on the frame the battle starts (time elapsed since the savefile was booted).</p>

<br>
<h4>General Requirements</h4>
<ul>
  <li><a href="https://mgba.io/downloads.html">mGBA emulator</a> (to play the game)</li>
  <li>Pokémon Emerald</li>
  <li><a href="https://github.com/Admiral-Fish/PokeFinder/releases">PokéFinder</a> (for timing calibration)</li>
  <li><a href="https://www.einarkl.no/Pokemon/RNGTimer/">RNGTimer</a> (for frame-based timer)</li>
</ul>
<br>
<h3>Latios</h3>
<p><span style="font-weight:bold">Goal:</span> Latios. Nature: Modest, IV: HP:29, Atk:21, Def:15, SpA:31, SpD:23, Spe:29.</p>

<h4>Requirements</h4>
<ul>
  <li>Eon Ticket (to access Southern Island)</li>
  <li>After defeating the Elite Four, picking Red as the color on the TV so Latias is roaming Hoenn (and Latios is in Southern Island)</li>
</ul>

<h4>How To</h4>
<div><span style="font-weight:bold">Target Frame:</span> 4571</div>
<div><span style="font-weight:bold">Stats:</span> Male, Modest, HP: 154 Atk:94, Def:92, SpA:165, SpD:126, Spe:129</div>

<ul>
  <li>Step 1: In PokéFinder, select Emerald, Gen 3 -> Static. Method: Method 1, Category: Legends, Pokémon: Latios. Filter: Check Show Stats. Press Generate.</li>
  <li>Step 2: Go to Southern Island and save right in front of Latios</li>
  <li>Step 3: On RNGTimer, select GBA mode, Frame 4571, Calibration 0.</li>
  <li>Step 4: Start the timer. When it reaches 0.000, reset the GBA (Start+Select+A+B).</li>
  <li>Step 5: When the timer reaches 0.000, press A to start Latios battle.</li>
  <li>Step 6: Catch Latios</li>
  <li>Step 7: Find the row matching the caught Latios <ul>
    <li>For example, if the caught Latios is Impish, HP: 143, Atk:95, Def: 99, SpA: 135, SpD: 124, Spe: 121; then this means the actual frame the A button was pressed is 4567.</li>
  </ul></li>

  <li>
    Step 8: In RNGTimer, write down the actual frame the A button was pressed in the "Frame hit" field, and press Update.
  </li>
  <li>
    Repeat Steps 4-8 until the caught Latios has the wanted stats (Male, Modest, HP:154, Atk:94, Def:92, SpA:165, SpD:126, Spe:129).
  </li>
</ul>

